products.title: Splash Flamingo Pink Panel Blind
products.description: Their moisture-resistant splash flamingo pink panel blinds have a stylish and modern feel that will update any space. The bold pink panel is a beautiful, contemporary colour which will brighten, and enrich the space with its warm, saturated shade. As panel blinds reach a massive 5 metres width and 3,. 5 metres drop, this makes it one of the largest blinds we make. A popular blind for large windows and doors, or as a modern room-divider, this blind is not only durable but versatile by design.

products.title: Splash Lipstick Pink Panel Blind
products.description: Their moisture-resistant, splash lipstick pink panel blinds are a fabulous way to dress your large window. The bold pink shade, adds flair and saturated colour which can make for a dramatic finish to your room. As their panel blinds are available at 5 metres width and 3 metres drop, panel blinds are a great way to divide a large room or to dress a large window. Panel blinds are perfect for patio doors & are available with a various control & stacking options, including a wand control making them inherently child safe.
